|title=Metallomics and the Cell |year=2013 |publisher=Springer |isbn=978-94-007-5561-1 |issn=1868-0402}}
</ref><ref name=AS>{{cite book |last=Shriver |first=D. F.|last2=Atkins |first2=P. W.|title=Inorganic chemistry|publisher=Oxford University Press|year=1999|edition=3rd|chapter=Chapter 19, Bioinorganic chemistry|isbn=0-19-850330-X }}</ref>。所有蛋白质中有大量是属于这一类。例如，尽管可能有多达3000种人类的锌金属蛋白质<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Andreini C, Banci L, Bertini I, Rosato A | title = Zinc through the three domains of life | journal = Journal of Proteome Research | volume = 5 | issue = 11 | pages = 3173–8 | date = November 2006 | pmid = 17081069 | doi = 10.1021/pr0603699 }}</ref>
